These are Puzzles for 2x6 Level 7

.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-7-1::.
The people perfer 6 different movie-genres: spy, zombie, sports, fantasy, disaster, crime
6 different pets are kept: cat, goldfish, guinea-pig, hedgehog, mouse, rabbit
 1. the person watching sports movies is in an odd position##4
 2. the person watching crime movies is somewhere to the left of the person watching zombie movies##5
 3. the person watching disaster movies is not the owner of the mouse##6
 4. the person watching fantasy movies is somewhere to the left of the person watching zombie movies##5
 5. the owner of the mouse is somewhere to the left of the owner of the guinea-pig##5
 6. the owner of the goldfish is somewhere to the right of the owner of the guinea-pig##5
 7. the owner of the mouse is not the person watching zombie movies##6
 8. the owner of the rabbit is in an odd position##4
 9. the person watching spy movies is somewhere between the owner of the rabbit and the person watching fantasy movies##7
10. the owner of the guinea-pig is on the left or right of the owner of the hedgehog##3
11. the owner of the rabbit is somewhere to the right of the owner of the cat##5
12. the owner of the rabbit is somewhere to the left of the owner of the hedgehog##5
13. the owner of the cat is the person watching spy movies##1
14. the owner of the guinea-pig is somewhere to the left of the person watching disaster movies##5
15. the person watching crime movies is the owner of the hedgehog##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1   |   2   |   3    |    4     |     5      |    6     |
| Movie-Genre   | fantasy   | spy | sports   | crime     | zombie    | disaster   |
| Pet           | mouse | cat   | rabbit | hedgehog | guinea-pig | goldfish |

