 9. the person who's sport is baseball is on the left or right of the musician##3
10. the person who's sport is surfing is somewhere between the bartender and the musician##7
11. the person who's sport is swimming is in an odd position##4
12. the person who's sport is baseball is on the left or right of the firefighter##3
13. the firefighter is somewhere to the left of the person who's sport is baseball##5
14. the project-manager is somewhere to the left of the person who's sport is swimming##5

.:: Answer ::.
