 3. the person who growsmarigold is somewhere to the right of the person drinking mirinda##5
 4. the person drinking 7up is on the right of the person drinking mirinda##1
 5. the person who growsmarigold is not the person drinking mirinda##6
 6. the person drinking hot-chocolate is somewhere between the person drinking water and the person drinking mirinda##7
 7. the person drinking hot-chocolate is somewhere between the person drinking 7up and the person drinking water##7
 8. the person drinking almond-milk is on the right of the person who growsbegonia##1
 9. the person who growszinnia is somewhere between the person drinking hot-chocolate and the person drinking lemonade##7
10. the person who growsdaisy is on the right of the person drinking lemonade##1
11. the person drinking mirinda is on the right of the person drinking hot-chocolate##1
12. the person who growsaconite is somewhere to the left of the person who growsmarigold##5
13. the person who growsbegonia is the person drinking lemonade##1
14. the person who growszinnia is somewhere to the left of the person drinking 7up##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |      2      |   3   |       4       |    5    |   6   |
