 5. the person who's sport is basketball is between the owner of the goldfish and the person who's sport is badminton##2
 6. the owner of the pony is on the far left or far right##3
 7. the person who's sport is badminton is somewhere to the left of the person who's sport is rowing##5
 8. the person who's sport is badminton is somewhere between the person who's sport is skateboarding and the person who's sport is golf##7
 9. the owner of the pony is on the left or right of the owner of the dog##3
10. the owner of the cat is on the far right##1
11. the owner of the goldfish is the person who's sport is biathlon##1
12. the owner of the ferret is not the person who's sport is biathlon##6
13. the owner of the dog is on the left of the owner of the goat##1
14. the owner of the ferret is the owner of the ferret##1

