 2. the person who's sport is climbing is the owner of the horse##1
 3. the owner of the frog is on the left or right of the owner of the guinea-pig##3
 4. the owner of the lizard is somewhere between the owner of the frog and the person who's sport is weightlifting##7
 5. the owner of the guinea-pig is somewhere between the owner of the goat and the owner of the lizard##7
 6. the owner of the mouse is somewhere to the right of the owner of the frog##5
 7. the owner of the mouse is on the right of the person who's sport is water-polo##1
 8. the owner of the frog is on the right of the owner of the guinea-pig##1
 9. the owner of the horse is somewhere to the right of the owner of the goat##5
10. the person who's sport is baseball is in an even position##4
11. the owner of the lizard is on the left or right of the person who's sport is handball##3
12. the owner of the horse is somewhere to the right of the person who's sport is baseball##5
13. the person who's sport is handball is on the left of the person who's sport is water-polo##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2     |    3     |     4      |       5       |    6     |
| Pet   | goat | guinea-pig | frog   | lizard  | mouse      | horse  |
| Sport         | rugby      | baseball | handball | water-polo | weightlifting | climbing |

