 3. the person who's hobby is traveling is somewhere to the right of the wooden house##5
 4. the person who's hobby is camping is somewhere between the palace house and the farmhouse house##7
 5. the cape-cod house is on the left or right of the wooden house##3
 6. the person who's hobby is drawing is the cottage house##1
