10. the farmhouse house is somewhere to the right of the cape-cod house##5
11. the cape-cod house is on the right of the wooden house##1
12. the person who's hobby is camping is somewhere to the right of the palace house##5
13. the person who's hobby is collecting is somewhere between the person who's hobby is camping and the person who's hobby is drawing##7
14. the farmhouse house is on the left of the person who's hobby is traveling##1
